OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1776355855
OL,3,CMental health trust leadership rating
OL,4,Cdowngraded to requires improvement
OL,6,FA healthcare regulator has downgraded
OL,7,Fthe rating for leadership at one of
OL,8,FEngland's largest mental health trusts
OL,9,Ffrom outstanding to requires
OL,10,Fimprovement.
OL,12,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,13,Fdecision follows an inspection in late
OL,14,F2025 at Cumbria, Northumberland, Tyne
OL,15,Fand Wear NHS Foundation Trust, which
OL,16,Fprovides many of the mental health
OL,17,Fservices across the region.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
