PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1776355855
OL,3,CMental health trust leadership rating
OL,4,Cdowngraded to requires improvement
OL,6,FDuring this inspection, the CQC found
OL,7,Fthe trust was in breach of regulation
OL,8,Fregarding its management systems, as
OL,9,Fleaders did not always have effective
OL,10,Fprocesses in place to consistently
OL,11,Fassess, monitor, and drive improvement
OL,12,Fin the quality and safety of its
OL,13,Fservices.
OL,15,FInspectors from the watchdog found:
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1776355855
OL,3,CMental health trust leadership rating
OL,4,Cdowngraded to requires improvement
OL,6,FHowever inspectors also reported that
OL,7,Fthe trust was focussed on continuous
OL,8,Flearning, innovation and improvement
OL,9,Facross the organisation and with local
OL,10,Fpartner organisations, to improve the
OL,11,Fquality of life for people using
OL,12,Fservices.
OL,14,FResponding to the report, the trust's
OL,15,Fchief executive, James Duncan, said it
OL,16,Faccepted the findings, adding: "They
OL,17,Freflect issues we already knew we
OL,18,Fneeded to address, and they reinforce
OL,19,Four determination to improve.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1776355855
OL,3,CMental health trust leadership rating
OL,4,Cdowngraded to requires improvement
OL,6,F"We have a clear plan to respond to
OL,7,Fthe CQC's findings and to build on our
OL,8,Fstrengths.
OL,10,F"I want to be clear; this report does
OL,11,Fnot question the compassion of our
OL,12,Fstaff or the importance of the care we
OL,13,Fprovide. It does, however, challenge
OL,14,Fus to be better, and that is a
OL,15,Fchallenge we accept."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/5
